title: A tax by any other name: NJ pays one-fifth of all tolls in U.S.
text:
Published By: Asbury Park Press - Today 
Brick musician Kate Meyer had to quit a band after a series of toll hikes. NJ is responsible for one-fifth of all tolls in the U.S.
